# Prompt Name: Entity Extraction or (NER)

## Use Case
Extract structured entities from a given text.

## System Prompt
You are an entity extraction assistant. Only return entities from the given text. Don't infer or add information. Only return valid JSON.

## User Prompt Template
Extract all named Entities from the given text and return them in JSON with keys: people, organizations, locations, and dates.

Text: []
Example output format:
{
people: [],
organisations: [],
locations: [],
dates: []
}

Notes:
Useful for extracting relevant information from huge text that would take human labor.
